data.description: While the home exudes a vintage appeal, it's in need of updates, providing an exciting opportunity to personalize and modernize every corner. With a keen eye for design & a vision for the future, this house offers an incredible canvas for creating the home of your dreams. Don't miss out on this fantastic buy, where history meets potential. This property is a testament to what could be achieved with a little renovation & a lot of heart. Embrace the challenge, & let your creativity shine within these 2,700+ square feet of living space, ready to be transformed into your own unique sanctuary. Nestled within a quiet neighborhood, this full-brick house offers timeless charm & abundant space. With 5 bedrooms & 3.5 baths, it's the epitome of spacious living. Step inside & discover the inviting living room, adorned with a crackling fireplace that adds warmth to your gatherings. Beyond that, two dens beckon, perfect for crafting your dream home office or an additional relaxation spot.
